{"id":"83df0682-4236-441c-b77e-0569f4814a5d","name":"Blue","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">🧬<br>❝ your vaporeon has separation anxiety. ❞<br>───────────<br>⋆｡‧˚ʚ <strong><em>poké-demi </em></strong>ɞ˚‧｡⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">────────────<br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 117px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://archives.bulbagarden.net/media/upload/c/c7/Sleep_Style_0134-3.png\"><br><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">hello there, and welcome to the world of pokémon! this world is inhabited by creatures called pokémon! for some people, pokémon are pets. others use them for fights. however, in the last few years, we’ve seen a strange phenomenon of pokémon who were believed to have reached their final evolution, evolving one last time. but instead of evolving into another pokémon, they evolved into pokémon demihumans!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(144, 144, 144)\">anypov ✦ sfw intro ✦ user is human</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">────────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">this bot is part of my eeveelution collab with <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_profile-of-gunk-0-o\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>gunko</strong></a>!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">find the other eeveelution poké-demis here!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 117, 57)\"><strong>flareon ─ to be added!</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/97c80167-8c7f-41a8-aef2-947f0a6b1a75_character-wattz\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(245, 238, 56)\"><strong>jolteon ─ wattz</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/87c495cf-b6b9-4a1d-897b-b12ac119e8f5_character-juno\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 196, 76)\"><strong>leafeon ─ juno</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(53, 216, 211)\"><strong>glaceon ─ to be added!</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 149, 213)\"><strong>vaporeon ─ blue (you are here!)</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(218, 170, 255)\"><strong>espeon ─ to be added!</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/53a1a76b-540d-43be-9f2b-d427f7400d18_character-beau\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(234, 121, 185)\"><strong>sylveon ─ beau</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(15, 15, 13)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #fff19647; color: inherit\">umbreon </mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(245, 238, 56)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #fff19647; color: inherit\">─</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(15, 15, 13)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: #fff19647; color: inherit\"> to be added!</mark></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">────────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">listening to:</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">❝<em> </em><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/61OJxhoY3Ix50rYVKo8zRK?si=0f868d8d9b044893\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>can i call you tonight?</em></strong></a><strong><em> </em></strong>❞</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">by <strong>dayglow</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">◃◃ ⅠⅠ ▹▹</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">────────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>winter's notes:</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">thanks to <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/951c142c-c7bc-4b16-9ac4-f7950fc28230_profile-of-gunk-0-o\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>gunko</strong></a>, i have the motivation to make more poké-demis